name: Kristera Mix
description:
So I wanted to do something different and take all these different images I’ve collected in different trainings and create something. This became the Mix person series.

I will be taking a sampling from multiple people and create a new character from that.

If you like this and want to help support me why not buy me a coffee

Below is a mix of the people this character contains:

  • Kristen Bell

  • Christina Aguilera

  • Lana Parrilla

  • Carmella
